<HEAD>AFL-CIO Hopes to Deliver Huge Margin of Union Votes to Dukakis</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By MATT YANCEY</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>AP Labor Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
