<TEXT>
 <PERSON> Kevin </PERSON> <PERSON> Noblet </PERSON> is <LOCATION> Santiago </LOCATION> bureau chief for <ORGANIZATION> The </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION>.
